---
import BaseLayout from '../layouts/BaseLayout.astro';
---

<BaseLayout title="About">
  <div class="container page-content">
    <div class="content-box">
      <h1>About WIAA</h1>
      
      <p class="intro">The Workforce in Agriculture and AI (WIAA) program at Iowa State University is dedicated to inspiring the next generation of leaders in agricultural technology and artificial intelligence.</p>

      <h2>Our Mission</h2>
      <p>WIAA aims to bridge the gap between traditional agriculture and emerging AI technologies by providing hands-on, engaging educational experiences for students of all ages. We believe that by introducing young people to the exciting possibilities at the intersection of agriculture and technology, we can cultivate a workforce ready to tackle the challenges of feeding a growing global population sustainably.</p>

      <h2>What We Do</h2>
      
      <h3>Educational Programs</h3>
      <p>We offer two main educational tracks:</p>
      <ul>
        <li><strong>Drone Program:</strong> Students learn about UAV technology, aerial imaging, and how drones are revolutionizing precision agriculture</li>
        <li><strong>Rover Program:</strong> Hands-on experience with ground-based robotics, sensors, and automated field monitoring systems</li>
      </ul>

      <h3>Outreach Initiatives</h3>
      <p>WIAA actively engages with schools, 4H groups, and community organizations throughout Iowa and beyond. Our outreach programs include:</p>
      <ul>
        <li>School visits and demonstrations</li>
        <li>Workshop facilitation</li>
        <li>Science fair support</li>
        <li>Educational resource development</li>
        <li>Professional development for educators</li>
      </ul>

      <h2>Our Team</h2>
      <p>WIAA is led by faculty and graduate students from Iowa State University's College of Agriculture and Life Sciences. Our team brings together expertise in agronomy, computer science, engineering, and education to create impactful learning experiences.</p>

      <h2>Partner With Us</h2>
      <p>We're always looking to expand our reach and impact. Whether you're an educator interested in bringing WIAA programming to your students, a researcher looking to collaborate, or an organization wanting to support agricultural education, we'd love to hear from you.</p>

      <div class="cta-section">
        <a href="/contact" class="btn btn-primary">Get in Touch</a>
        <a href="/outreach" class="btn btn-secondary" style="margin-left: 15px;">View Our Programs</a>
      </div>
    </div>
  </div>
</BaseLayout>

<style>
  .page-content {
    padding: 60px 20px;
  }

  .content-box {
    background: white;
    padding: 40px;
    border-radius: 8px;
    border: 1px solid var(--border-light);
    max-width: 900px;
    margin: 0 auto;
  }

  .content-box h1 {
    margin-bottom: 20px;
    border-bottom: 2px solid var(--isu-gold);
    padding-bottom: 15px;
  }

  .intro {
    font-size: 1.1em;
    color: var(--text-medium);
    line-height: 1.8;
    margin-bottom: 30px;
    font-weight: 500;
  }

  .content-box h2 {
    color: var(--isu-red);
    margin: 40px 0 20px;
    font-size: 1.6em;
  }

  .content-box h3 {
    color: var(--isu-red);
    margin: 25px 0 15px;
    font-size: 1.2em;
  }

  .content-box p {
    line-height: 1.7;
    margin-bottom: 15px;
  }

  .content-box ul {
    margin: 15px 0 20px 20px;
    line-height: 1.8;
  }

  .content-box li {
    margin-bottom: 10px;
  }

  .cta-section {
    text-align: center;
    margin-top: 50px;
    padding-top: 30px;
    border-top: 2px solid var(--border-light);
  }
</style>